[b]Bibata[/b] Cursor Theme with [b]semi-animated[/b] zebra stripes. This Cursor is built with [b][url=https://github.com/ful1e5/clickgen]clickgen[/url][/b] and render with the [b][url=https://github.com/puppeteer/puppeteer/]puppeteer[/url][/b].

[color=#ff0000][b]NOTES :[/b][/color]
[color=#ff0000]------------------------------[/color]
[b]* Why package size is so huge: [color=#008000](~200 MB)[/color][/b]
--- 1. Each cursors contains ~23 frames with HiDPi support.
--- 2. Animated cursors like '[i]left_ptr_watch[/i]' & '[i]wait[/i]' rendered with [b]high frames [/b]than usual.

[b]*[/b] Some cursors are not contains any animation: '[i]crossed_circle[/i]', '[i]wayland_cursor[/i]', '[i]x_cursor[/i]'
[color=#ff0000]------------------------------[/color]

[i][b]Bibata Zebra Styles: [/b][/i]
[i]Bibata Zebra Modern[/i]: Round Edges Bibata Zebra Cursors
[i]Bibata Zebra Original[/i]: Sharp Edges Bibata Zebra Cursors

[i]Available Sizes[/i] [b]22, 24, 28, 32, 40, 48, 56, 64, 72, 80, 88, 96[/b]
