[b]Linux/X11 installation[/b]
Get the latest stable Linux release from the [b][url=https://www.pling.com/p/1570301/]Pling[/url][/b]. Unpack [b].tar.gz[/b] file and follow these [b]commands[/b].

[b]Install[/b]
[b]For all user:[/b]
[code]sudo mv Bibata-Zebra-* /usr/share/icons[/code]
[b]For local user:
[/b][code]mv Bibata-Zebra-* ~/.icons[/code]

[b]Uninstall[/b]
[b]From all user:[/b]
[code]sudo rm -r /usr/share/icons/Bibata-Zebra-*[/code]
[b]From local user:[/b]
[code]rm -r ~/.icons/Bibata-Zebra-*[/code]

[size=150][b]Window installation[/b][/size]
[list=1]
    [*]unzip [b].zip[/b] file[/*]
    [*]Open [b]unziped[/b] directory in Explorer, and [b]right-click[/b] on [b]install.inf[/b].[/*]
    [*]Click 'Install' from the context menu, and authorize the modifications to your system.[/*]
    [*]Open [i]Control Panel > Personalisation and Appearance > Change mouse pointers[/i], and select [b]Bibata Zebra Cursors[/b].[/*]
    [*]Click '[b]Apply[/b]'.[/*]
[/list]

